"The town hall light was installed at the time, because it secures the school path," Eckert explained yesterday.
The Kluser traffic light secured both cyclists and bus passengers as well as the Bergle residents.
The plant officially commissioned yesterday is important for the crossroads Sulzbachweg/Kirchstraße.
