Lawyers must maintain the highest standards of integrity and ensure trust and confidence in the public.
Ditta has lost this trust and tried to hide behind the facade of his profession.
The Serious and Organized Crime Unit of Lancashire led the investigations against Ditta, which also led to a conviction in three cases for possession of cocaine and obstruction of justice, which underscores our determination to bring criminals to justice.
This case should be a warning to criminals and shows that no one can escape the arm of the law.
We will find you and bring you to court.
